snippet.title: Rahul Gandhi Dares PM Modi to Come to Parliament and Speak over Note Ban

localized.description:
Congress vice-president Rahul Gandhi dares PM Modi to come to Parliament and speak over note ban. Nitish Kumar and JD(U) are supporting PM Modi's demonetisation decision. BJP attacked Congress and other opposition parties for calling 'Bharat Bandh'.
